children.summary: Attempts to retrieve from the cache, and if present, removes the metadata from the cache.

summary: Caches message metadata for xUnit.net v3 messages. The metadata which is cached depends on the message that is passed (for example, looking up with an will return an ). Storage methods require the "Starting" versions of messages (as these are the ones which contain the metadata), and removal methods require the "Finished" versions of messages.
